---
description: Rules for Dio, cookies, API sessions, Manticore requests, and request handling
globs:
  - lib/**/*.dart
---

- Network code must go through the shared Dio layer.
- Session-aware requests must preserve cookies and existing auth/session behavior.
- `lib/services/manticore_search_service.dart` should reuse existing HTTP/session behavior instead of introducing an isolated client unless explicitly required.
- Do not create duplicate API clients or duplicate interceptors.
- Surface loading, error, and retry states explicitly.
- shared_preferences may store lightweight flags only, not critical session truth.
- When changing request/response models, update parsing and failure handling together.
